\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{B}_{r}(\mathbf{p}_{i})=\{\mathbf{p}_{i}\in\mathbf{P}^{\mathrm{in}}|\bigparallel\mathbf{r}_{i,j}\bigparallel\leq r\}$
